Package: tidysoilptf
Title: Tidy Pedotransfer Functions for Soil Hydraulic Property Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Einar Emil", "Låker", , "einaremil1999@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-5872-4959"))
Description: A tidy collection of pedotransfer functions (PTFs) for estimating
    soil hydraulic properties from basic soil data. Provides pipe-compatible
    functions returning tibbles with tidy evaluation support. Implements major
    parametric PTFs (Wösten 1999, Saxton & Rawls 2006, Vereecken 1989,
    Weynants 2009, Cosby 1984, Rawls & Brakensiek 1985) alongside bulk density
    estimators, parameter model converters (Campbell/Brooks-Corey to VGM), and
    physical plausibility checks. Every PTF stores training-domain metadata and
    automatically warns when inputs fall outside the PTF's calibration range.
